reviews.review_text: Nice Work The true value of a great Matrix patch. The moment the Cumberland patch to the Aud occurs, we are suddenly in the middle of the tapers, our feet in the grass and our ears in disbelief.

finally discovered matrix mixes been on arch9ive now a good year, ive been a bit behind on the technological scope a bit. these matrixes are what im lookking for now and always thougth a sbd&aud mix would be too cool.
cant wait to listen to this show i love so much now as a matrix. here we go!
